VALUES ('glossary-1101', 'alice-in-wonderland', 'jug', 'a large bottle with a narrow mouth', 'The Hatter was the only one who got any advantage from the change: and Alice was a good deal worse off than before, as the March Hare had just upset the milk-jug into his plate.', NULL);
