VALUES ('glossary-1102', 'alice-in-wonderland', 'examine', 'observe, check out, and look over carefully or inspect', '''May it please your Majesty,'' said Two, in a very humble tone, going down on one knee as he spoke, ''we were trying—'' ''I see!'' said the Queen, who had meanwhile been examining the roses.', NULL);
